Can't I say hello?

61
00:02:07,709 --> 00:02:09,009
I guess. It's just Santana

62
00:02:09,077 --> 00:02:10,427
told me never
to speak alone with you

63
00:02:10,512 --> 00:02:12,379
because you would try
to steal all of my gold.

64
00:02:12,430 --> 00:02:16,183
Okay, uh... anyway,
I got you this.

65
00:02:16,250 --> 00:02:18,469
I know everyone's always
making fun of your lips,

66
00:02:18,553 --> 00:02:20,471
