and I think your lips are cute,

69
00:02:24,776 --> 00:02:27,895
I was wondering if you would
go to to prom with me?

70
00:02:27,946 --> 00:02:29,146
As in your date?
Yeah.

71
00:02:29,214 --> 00:02:32,366
No.
No... "No, No" as in...?

72
00:02:32,433 --> 00:02:34,051
As in no prom.
Oh.

73
00:02:34,119 --> 00:02:35,435
I don't think I'm going.

74
00:02:35,487 --> 00:02:37,738
Are you worried
that Finn will be jealous?

75
00:02:37,789 --> 00:02:42,159
Look, you're just
not my type, okay, Rachel?

76
00:02:42,243 --> 00:02:45,245
So thanks for the lip chap.

77
00:02:47,677 --> 00:02:50,628
I feel like my life
finally has purpose.

78
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:53,682
It's so nice to be a part of a
cause that's bigger than myself.

79
00:02:53,766 --> 00:02:56,151
Honey Badger, I am so thrilled,

80
00:02:56,235 --> 00:02:57,936
Can I ask why you're dressed
like David Bowie?

81
00:02:58,004 --> 00:02:59,187
I'm incognito.

82
00:02:59,272 --> 00:03:00,822
