149
00:05:26,621 --> 00:05:28,188
Haven't you read <i>The Muckraker?</i>

150
00:05:28,239 --> 00:05:29,573
It's our school's newspaper.

151
00:05:29,658 --> 00:05:33,043
Look at the "Blind Items" column.

152
00:05:33,073 --> 00:05:34,432
"What prom queen candidate is spending

153
00:05:34,462 --> 00:05:35,967
a lot of time in her closet?"

154
00:05:35,997 --> 00:05:37,669
