good bands break up.

198
00:07:26,140 --> 00:07:29,464
But they put all that drama
to good use and wrote great music.

199
00:07:29,494 --> 00:07:32,979
You know, I think I might have
<i>Rumours</i> on LP somewhere.

200
00:07:33,031 --> 00:07:34,915
Oh, everybody does.

201
00:07:34,982 --> 00:07:36,888
