Kidding! Ha! Nope.

203
00:07:38,586 --> 00:07:40,003
I actually did that.

204
00:07:40,088 --> 00:07:41,505
Here we go.

205
00:07:41,589 --> 00:07:44,675
You know, I've wanted to
do a whole lesson devoted

206
00:07:44,759 --> 00:07:48,295
to a single album for a long time.

207
00:07:48,346 --> 00:07:51,431
You know, this is a
really good idea, April.

208
00:07:51,499 --> 00:07:53,801
And I'm here to help.

209
